
  Splunk Assistant Skills Demo
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------

  Indexes:   demo_devops, demo_sre, demo_support, demo_business
  Data:      7 days of realistic log data (~1M events)
  Session:   1 hour

  Example prompts to try:

    "Show me all errors in the last hour"
    "Which CI/CD pipelines failed today?"
    "Find the session trace for customer cust_456"
    "What's the P99 latency for the payment service?"
    "Show daily revenue trends by region"

  Access:
    Splunk Web UI: /splunk/ (in browser)
    Grafana:       /grafana/ (in browser)
    Webhooks:      /webhooks/ (view alert triggers)

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
